{"tid":2438489,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"姓「True」外國用戶   因 iCloud 程式漏洞導致無法使用","createTime":"2021-03-08T14:02:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-09T12:07:55.000Z","uid":66271,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"e48d790764baf9ef0ae837815d7d717407904a61","tid":2438489,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T14:02:03.000Z","msg":"由於用戶人數不少，只要 Apple 的雲端服務 iCloud 出現問題，都有機會影響全球很多人。最近 iCloud 又爆出現小問題，不過可能只得極少數人受影響，外國傳媒日前報導一名演員兼作家的 iCloud 帳號被上鎖超過半年，原因與 iCloud 的程式漏洞有關。<br />\n<br />\n這位名叫 Rachel True 的演員是 iCloud 用戶，但她的姓氏「True」卻被 iCloud 程式誤以為是程式中用作分辨正確與錯誤的 Boolean（布林數據類型），而非文本字串。由於 iCloud 程式出現上述問題，導致 True 無法正常使用 iCloud 超過 6 個月，期間她嘗試跟 Apple 的客戶服務員解釋，但 Apple 依然繼續向她收取月費；假如她將服務計劃轉成免費級別，她先前儲存的文件則會因此消失。<br />\nTrue 無計可施下只好在 Twitter 上載她的遭遇，由於她的特殊情況被傳媒廣泛報導，最後 Apple 主動聯絡她，表示會在本週內嘗試為她解決問題。"},{"pid":"9f0211a52c94ca4fa651d9fd4db27c5a4e5ba83a","tid":2438489,"uid":73241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T14:02:18.000Z","msg":"真"},{"pid":"53659a9b940d3a61cc088a66cdf78af31cba1405","tid":2438489,"uid":25062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T14:03:03.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"f889faf0a21af16352e2cb546b9123f94359a2e3","tid":2438489,"uid":74171,"like":36,"dislike":1,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T14:04:38.000Z","msg":"唯有叫 If Then Else"},{"pid":"f871592620f95ee793200259137500fab06a6e8b","tid":2438489,"uid":82562,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T14:06:51.000Z","msg":"改姓 null <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2789632662b8a8919c6d4e0b328c84b0899381a9","tid":2438489,"uid":68728,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T23:47:27.000Z","msg":"用家問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afb9b0d8d187bcdc5a209a09ff53d24b5d264d75","tid":2438489,"uid":30411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T01:05:32.000Z","msg